&lt;h2 id=&#34;wordpress-integration&#34;&gt;Wordpress Integration&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Vanilla&amp;rsquo;s integration to Wordpress lets you do a few things:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SSO from Wordpress to Vanilla&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use Vanilla as a commenting system on your Wordpress blog&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add a widget to your Wordpress site.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

